summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of $61.00 from the Excess Tax Sale Deposit Fund, and ordering the same paid to the Lucas Troendle and William Thomas owners of lot three (3), Block eight (8), Carles Supplemental Plat of D. T. Denny's Second Addition to the City of Seattle, sold for Eastlake Avenue condemnation assessment under Ordinance No. 6594.
